      "post_content": "If not used in a specific combo, this mechanic is garbage. It would die to destroy effects, or single burn spells, to larger creatures, get stolen, sacrificed, a pacifism slapped on, exiled or whatever.   \n  \nIt is playable though in a deck with.. uhm... [pyrohemia](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=pyrohemia) for example. The pyro won't kill it, and the ogre keeps the pyro in play.",
